sub_title: Chemical Engineering and Chemistry at Eindhoven University of Technology
summary:
I am a creative, open minded BSc Chemical Engineering graduate with analytical
thinking. I am inspired to use my knowledge and skills towards a more sustainable
world and contribute to the energy transition. With a good understanding in material
science and molecular systems, I am seeking to direct my career towards an
environmental organization where I can cooperate with other passionate engineers and
deliver solutions. I am experienced in working in either theoretical or practical team
projects and I usually bring an uplifting, positive atmosphere in the room.
